{"tid":1148792,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家公司點呀","createTime":"2019-05-10T16:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T13:44:20.000Z","uid":234147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b1b182d17358215526be9585570a70cbe94eeb56","tid":1148792,"uid":234147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T16:31:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n做緊PT放題侍應<br />\n今日星期五做到成個智障咁<br />\n想知大家公司好唔好做來平衡下<br />\n我公司係爛檔<br />\n老細想請人搵錢<br />\n但係唔肯搵錢請人<br />\n搞到個場成日都唔夠人<br />\n然後成日捽數<br />\n我都明白我係老細可能會閪過佢<br />\n但係有時做下樣扮體恤下都好吖<br />\n利申過多兩個月唔撚做呀DLGH<br />\n仲有各位同行<br />\n千祈咪撚做放題呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7006195a1c18038c799e1f19f5a30c48e8878bd4","tid":1148792,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T16:32:19.000Z","msg":"人工幾多？"},{"pid":"ba4b4d90db488e4ac43b0c111e6e4300c25a5ee9","tid":1148792,"uid":234147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7006195a1c18038c799e1f19f5a30c48e8878bd4","tid":1148792,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T16:32:19.000Z","msg":"人工幾多？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T16:32:45.000Z","msg":"6x蚊個鍾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8747402f451bda77fd0570e195435540108cb026","tid":1148792,"uid":234147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T17:06:35.000Z","msg":"理我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8bb2e670a36be2e5bf95b5517a6aeb44ae1b2b2","tid":1148792,"uid":35852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T17:30:34.000Z","msg":"好hea, 但人工低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8347fc17d477f3e796acb5957740d94e7661174","tid":1148792,"uid":234147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8bb2e670a36be2e5bf95b5517a6aeb44ae1b2b2","tid":1148792,"uid":35852,"like":0,"dislike"